{"tid":1632103,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"victim blaming?針對淺藍同中立燃可行嗎？","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:59:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T04:29:00.000Z","uid":280899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2a15586e68a5b1d5daf3a22532f12d4c1ffd7210","tid":1632103,"uid":280899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:59:37.000Z","msg":"想問下大家意見，<br />\n之前睇過人類有種奇妙心態叫victim blaming，<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中文叫受害者責備，<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n意思大約係，明明對方先係受害者，<br />\n但很多時反而會比人屌番轉頭，<br />\n<br />\n可以引用番對付d無知淺藍同中文燃嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如，<br />\n班後生仔輸左，到時齊齊比呀爺清算，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你估搞到咁大鑊，呀爺會放過大家咩？你同呀爺講自己無辜，睇下佢會唔會放過你?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n阻到你返工放工係唔好，但係一輸左都係大家一鑊熟，<br />\n你就出少句聲，行多兩步當幫助，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係呀！嫁下明綁架你，唔比你返工呀！有本事同柒婆講，佢會聽就唔會唔搞到咁!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之類<br />\n好處，希望可以策返依班沉默大多數!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文筆唔好，希望個意思帶到比大家，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n目標，偏中立一群，有無幫助?<br />\nand有無手足討論下點優化?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e34c4bc0fd4af5dceb575adff7b98e9611300eb9","tid":1632103,"uid":280899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:20.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"131aba61aeac76c1a875abd3c333116e40f5e9a5","tid":1632103,"uid":280899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:29:00.000Z","msg":"推"}]}